/sle-2017/sle-2017-papers-artifact-evaluation-committee">AEC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/ThomasDegueule.html">Thomas Degueule</a> (<a href="https://conf.researchr.org/committee/sle-2017/sle-2017-papers-artifact-evaluation-committee">AEC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/LukasDiekmann.html">Lukas Diekmann</a> (<a href="https://conf.researchr.org/committee/sle-2017/sle-2017-papers-artifact-evaluation-committee">AEC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/RominaEramo.html">Romina Eramo</a> (<a href="https://conf.researchr.org/committee/sle-2017/sle-2017-papers-artifact-evaluation-committee">AEC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/AbelGómez.html">Abel Gómez</a> (<a href="https://conf.researchr.org/committee/sle-2017/sle-2017-papers-artifact-evaluation-committee">AEC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/ThomasKühn.html">Thomas Kühn</a> (<a href="https://conf.researchr.org/committee/sle-2017/sle-2017-papers-artifact-evaluation-committee">AEC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/ManuelLeduc.html">Manuel Leduc</a> (<a href="https://conf.researchr.org/committee/sle-2017/sle-2017-papers-artifact-evaluation-committee">AEC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/JulianMackay.html">Julian Mackay</a> (<a href="https://conf.researchr.org/committee/sle-2017/sle-2017-papers-artifact-evaluation-committee">AEC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/TanjaMayerhofer.html">Tanja Mayerhofer</a> (<a href="https://conf.researchr.org/committee/sle-2017/sle-2017-papers-artifact-evaluation-committee">Artefact Evaluation Chair</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/MatthewRoberts.html">Matthew Roberts</a> (<a href="https://conf.researchr.org/committee/sle-2017/sle-2017-papers-artifact-evaluation-committee">AEC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/VascoSousa.html">Vasco Sousa</a> (<a href="https://conf.researchr.org/committee/sle-2017/sle-2017-papers-artifact-evaluation-committee">AEC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/DanielStrüber.html">Daniel Strüber</a> (<a href="https://conf.researchr.org/committee/sle-2017/sle-2017-papers-artifact-evaluation-committee">AEC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/MatúšSulír.html">Matúš Sulír</a> (<a href="https://conf.researchr.org/committee/sle-2017/sle-2017-papers-artifact-evaluation-committee">AEC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/AnaMariaSutii.html">Ana Maria Sutii</a> (<a href="https://conf.researchr.org/committee/sle-2017/sle-2017-papers-artifact-evaluation-committee">AEC</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/LaurenceTratt.html">Laurence Tratt</a> (<a href="https://conf.researchr.org/committee/sle-2017/sle-2017-papers-artifact-evaluation-committee">Artefact Evaluation Chair</a>)</li><li><a href="../profile/AndreasWortmann.html">Andreas Wortmann</a> (<a href="https://conf.researchr.org/committee/sle-2017/sle-2017-papers-artifact-evaluation-committee">AEC</a>)</li></ul>
